<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Village PM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/footer.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/galerie.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="part-1">
            <img class="logo-header" src="assets/img/village-pm-white.png" alt="Logo Village PM">
        </div>
        <div class="part-2">
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Feed</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>1 PM</h1>
        </section>
        
        <section class="scroll-3d">
            <canvas id="canvas"></canvas>

            <div class="text text-1">
                <h1>LIKE A SECOND SKIN</h1>
                <p>A progressive, precise <br> skateboard shoe for ultimate fit, <br> comfort and support.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text text-2">
                <p>Easy to break in, with soft, sticky climbing rubber that flicks just right wrapped around the toes and heel.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text text-3">
                <p>But the 1PM was designed to go far beyond that. To last an entire day, not just a single session. To transition from one moment to the next, without ever having to change.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="scroll-content"></div>
        </section>
        
        <!-- SPACER POUR PERMETTRE LE SCROLL À TRAVERS LE PRODUCT VIEWER FIXE -->
        <div class="product-viewer-spacer"></div>
        
        <!-- PRODUCT VIEWER (FIXE PENDANT LE SCROLL) -->
        <section class="product-viewer">
            <div class="viewer-wrapper">
                <!-- GAUCHE: BOUTONS + DESCRIPTIONS -->
                <div class="viewer-left">
                    <h2>A CLOSER LOOK</h2>
                    <div class="left-content">
                        <div class="buttons-list">
                            <button class="control-btn active" data-index="0">
                                <span class="btn-label">ADJUSTMENT & FIT</span>
                                <p class="btn-description" style="display: none;">Thanks to its "Rubber Glove" technology, the 1PM uses non-vulcanized rubber that is both flexible, grippy and durable. Hand-shaped, it wraps your foot like a second skin and m...</p>
                            </button>
                            <button class="control-btn" data-index="1">
                                <span class="btn-label">CONTROL & FEEL</span>
                                <p class="btn-description" style="display: none;">The forefoot, reinforced with a climbing-inspired rubber rand, provides grip and precision where every move counts, while the EVA midsole delivers heel cushioning and a thin p...</p>
                            </button>
                            <button class="control-btn" data-index="2">
                                <span class="btn-label">COMFORT & CONVENIENCE</span>
                                <p class="btn-description" style="display: none;">Heel pull tabs make it easy to slip on the 1PM in an instant. Zero seams minimize discomfort, while traditional comfort comes from quality materials throughout.</p>
                            </button>
                            <button class="control-btn" data-index="3">
                                <span class="btn-label">DURABILITY & MATERIALS</span>
                                <p class="btn-description" style="display: none;">Built to last through an entire day, not just a single session. Premium materials and expert construction ensure the 1PM maintains its performance and aesthetic.</p>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- DIVIDER -->
                <div class="viewer-divider"></div>

                <!-- DROITE: CANVAS 3D -->
                <div class="viewer-right">
                    <div class="canvas-container">
                        <canvas id="viewer-canvas"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section>
            <%- include('partials/galerie') %>
        </section>
        <section>
            <%- include('partials/footer') %>
        </section>
    </main>

    <!-- SCRIPTS CDN -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/gsap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.2/ScrollTrigger.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lenis@1.0.45/dist/lenis.min.js"></script>

    <!-- THREE.JS MODULE (type="module" obligatoire) -->
    <script type="module" src="assets/js/script-threejs.js"></script>
    
    <!-- Scripts non-module -->
    <script src="assets/js/footer.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/galerie.js"></script>
</body>
</html>